# Optimization #3: Eliminate strconv.FormatInt allocations in Increment

## Implementation
- Added pre-formatted string constants for common integer values (0, 1, -1, 60, 300, 3600, 86400)
- Created formatInt() and FormatInt64() functions that use constants when possible
- Updated FormatFlagInt() to use formatInt() instead of strconv.Itoa()
- Updated Increment() to use meta.FormatInt64() instead of strconv.FormatInt()

